text:
Choco-senpai and Juri-chan,
do you have any Valentine's Day memories?

You gave me chocolates the other day, right?
You said, "It's a bit early", though.

Wow, I'm glad you certified them as delicious!
That's right!

I thought it was quite early.
Why was that?

During Valentine's season, the store only has Valentine's
products. The ones the other day were regular items!

I wanted you to eat both because I like them!
Look forward to the actual day too!

Is that so!?
I'm really looking forward to it!

Everything Choco-senpai gives me
to eat is delicious...!
